---
title: Cheesy Tex-Mex Chicken Nachos with Tomato-Spinach Salsa & Yoghurt
description: Feeling the need for muchos nachos? Make everyone in the house happy tonight with these easy homemade tortilla chips, cheesy Tex-Mex chicken, salsa and sour cream.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65765a28a65f6d71569fae5c-90118868.jpeg
